genresAdvancedInfo.name: neo-trad prog
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Neo-trad prog is a contemporary take on traditional progressive rock, blending complex instrumentation, unconventional time signatures, and intricate song structures with modern production techniques. This genre incorporates elements of jazz, classical, and world music to create a unique and dynamic sound that appeals to fans of both classic and modern prog.
